# DevPath Startup

### 1. Model (Ollama)

```powershell
ollama list
ollama serve
ollama run llama3.1:8b
```

### 2. Backend

```powershell
cd devpath-backend
.\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run "-Dspring-boot.run.profiles=local"
```

### 3. Frontend

```powershell
cd devpath-frontend
npm run dev
```

Start order:

```text
Model → Backend → Frontend
```
